{{Otheruses|Combine}}
An '''agro-combine''' was a place where livestock and crops were raised and harvested. The world of [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]] boasted a number of agro-combines, as did other worlds noted for producing large quantities of foodstuffs. [[Soontir Fel/Legends|Soontir Fel]] worked for an agro-combine for a time before entering the [[Imperial Academy/Legends|Imperial Academy]]. As a child [[Delak Krennel]] was involved in the destruction of farmland owned by [[Alien/Legends|aliens]] on Corellia, which would later be used for agro-combines.<ref name="XwLIR">''[[X-Wing: Isard's Revenge]]''</ref>

The [[Allied Grain and Roughage]] agro-combines of Corellia held annual [[Harvest Festival]]s to celebrate the harvest.

{{Company-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
Agro-combines seem to be the ''Star Wars'' equivalent of real-world corporate farms.

